Margaret Anglin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Anglin 0 Mary Margaret Warren Anglin (April 3, 1876 – January 7, 1958) was a Canadian-born Broadway actress, director and producer. Encyclopædia Britannica calls "one of the most brilliant actresses of her day."
